# Fastlane plugins for Alfanumrik Android.
#
# No third-party plugins are required: upload_to_play_store ships with core
# fastlane (the `supply` action). This file exists so `bundle exec fastlane`
# resolves a Pluginfile without warning and so future plugins have a home.
#
# To add a plugin: `bundle exec fastlane add_plugin <name>` (it will append here).
